#. (growing)'}
#: .\items.json
msgid ""
"A garden pot growing some tasty, unnameable plants.  You shouldn't see this "
"item."
msgstr "一个花园盆，里面种着一些美味但无法命名的植物。你不应该看到这个物品。"

