#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Growable Garden Pots"
msgstr "可种植花园盆"

#. ~ Description for Growable Garden Pots
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Allows you to grow seeds of 12 different plants in craftable garden pots "
"that can be carried around as items.  Perfect for the nomadic botanist."
msgstr "允许你在可制作的花园盆中种植12种不同植物的种子，这些盆可作为物品携带。非常适合游牧植物学家。"
